              YOUTUBE COMPLIANCE ADDENDUM
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

This addendum forms part of the license for PawTube and must be preserved
in all copies, forks, and derivative works of the Software.

1. YOUTUBE TERMS OF SERVICE COMPLIANCE
   ─────────────────────────────────────
   PawTube is designed to operate in full compliance with YouTube's Terms of
   Service (https://www.youtube.com/t/terms) and YouTube's API Services Terms
   of Service (https://developers.google.com/youtube/terms/api-services-tos).

   Contributors and users of this Software agree to:

   a) Not use PawTube to download, cache, store, or reproduce YouTube video
      content outside of what is expressly permitted by YouTube's Terms.

   b) Not modify or redistribute this Software in any way that circumvents,
      bypasses, or violates YouTube's Terms of Service, Community Guidelines,
      or embedded player policies.

   c) Not use this Software to strip, block, or interfere with YouTube's
      monetization systems, including but not limited to advertisements
      served outside of the embedded player context.

   d) Acknowledge that all video content accessed through PawTube remains
      the property of its respective content creators and YouTube/Google LLC,
      and is subject to their respective copyright and licensing terms.

2. USE OF YOUTUBE PRIVACY-ENHANCED EMBED (youtube-nocookie.com)
   ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   PawTube exclusively uses the YouTube Privacy-Enhanced Embed mode via
   the domain:

       https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/

   This is an official embedding method provided by YouTube/Google LLC and
   is used here solely to improve user privacy by not setting cookies unless
   the user explicitly interacts with the embedded player.

   Use of youtube-nocookie.com is permitted and recognized by YouTube's
   official embed documentation. PawTube makes no claim of ownership over
   the embedded player, its interface, or any content served through it.

3. NO AFFILIATION DISCLAIMER
   ──────────────────────────
   PawTube is an independent, open-source project and is NOT affiliated with,
   endorsed by, sponsored by, or officially connected to YouTube, Google LLC,
   or Alphabet Inc. in any way.

   The name "YouTube" and associated logos are trademarks of Google LLC.
   All rights to these trademarks remain with their respective owners.

4. FORKS AND DERIVATIVE WORKS
   ────────────────────────────
   Any fork, modification, or derivative work of this Software must:

   a) Retain this YouTube Compliance Addendum in its entirety.
   b) Continue to use only lawful and officially supported YouTube
      embedding mechanisms.
   c) Not represent itself as being affiliated with or approved by
      YouTube or Google LLC.
   d) Update the copyright line to clearly credit the original author
      (SKY / PawDevs) while distinguishing the derivative work.

5. USER RESPONSIBILITY
   ─────────────────────
   End users are solely responsible for ensuring their use of PawTube
   complies with the laws of their jurisdiction and the Terms of Service
   of any third-party platforms accessed through the Software, including
   but not limited to YouTube.

